<s> Hi Gregory, What you propose below is that user agents bypass the standard Windows task control mechanism (which is apparently buggy).  </s>
<s> I have problems with this technique since it seems to contract the checkpoint that requires user agents to use standard controls of the operating system.  </s>
<s> If the Windows mechanism is buggy, it should be fixed.  </s>
<s> I don't think we should ask Windows UAs to reimplement something as basic as the task navigation tool.  </s>
<s> Furthermore, this seems to be out of scope for user agents - we should not require them to track all Windows of the operating system.  </s>
